Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.09,0:01:59.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I happened to witness \Nsomething outrageous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:04.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what people call...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"a love triangle exposed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:12.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Min-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.79,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.24,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me. \NDon't even breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.36,0:02:28.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But then I'll die...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:31.09,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.59,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:35.54,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.76,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Has something happened, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.35,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:52.85,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.19,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,But why Fukuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just so lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:57.39,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.46,0:03:01.13,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,...telling me about this in greater detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fetch me a grater from storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:21.18,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:27.14,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's late today, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's not coming in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.66,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I need that grater {\i1}now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.50,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 5: A Tearful Chef Romance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He's been offered a better job elsewhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:48.59,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I've concluded
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the information I've gathered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.60,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,What information?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.60,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was more suited to writing a detective novel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.60,0:03:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than erotica.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.29,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,In order to write my novel with
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this shabby hot spring district as the background,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:03.56,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been gathering information
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the people here and their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:08.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, a detective novel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.56,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.32,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,We need to \Ndiscuss Tohru's job offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.86,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Who cares"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.10,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.16,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our manager and Fukuya's manager
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have been rivals for a long time now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.73,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I've heard the rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:32.40,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, while looking for a way to crush Kissuiso,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:34.96,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuya spotted Tohru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:37.71,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,The loss of a talented chef would be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a huge blow to Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.30,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Then that must've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.25,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.14,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure, Mr. Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.52,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be okay without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.74,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep things going here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when you're not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.97,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:12.89,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,I think he might've been discussing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his job offer with Mr. Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.36,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuya is a four star inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.99,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,People have a brighter future \Nworking there than here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we don't get as much business as them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's saying too much, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:24.97,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ren pointed Tohru, \Nwho has great talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,towards a better path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.64,0:05:29.23,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's my conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:31.14,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even have the chance \Nto throw a farewell party for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:36.57,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,But Tohru sure is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.68,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's already gotten friendly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with the successor to Fukuya-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.27,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.61,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.95,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,He may appear abrupt and cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.04,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality he treasures \Nthe people working here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his job more than anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:55.28,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that \NTohru would do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.77,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to be killed with a grater?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.67,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Let's ask him ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.99,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, Tohru isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.07,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,He's not in today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.22,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,We were too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:10.55,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,He's flown the coop...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:13.35,Default,Jiro,0000,0000,0000,,leaving us behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:19.74,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.34,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,The white croaker will soon be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.11,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,How's the pepper leaf bud doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.53,0:06:29.55,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be finished soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:33.40,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did Tohru leave for Fukuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:40.12,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious about \Nbeing a chef too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.20,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.14,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll eventually find out the answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:45.25,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.98,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,That's what happens \Nwhen you don't focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.93,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. \NI'll finish cutting these-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.93,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:53.23,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,handling the customers' \Nfood with your hand like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:56.99,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do the rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.57,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. This is a pretty bad case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:07.91,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Although, you can't exactly blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:10.19,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Her savior's no longer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:11.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Her savior?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.80,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,The one who allowed her to work here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was Tohru actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:21.55,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, \NMinko wanted to be a chef
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without even attending high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:26.30,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,However, her parents were against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.09,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,She refused to give up her dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she started \Nlooking for places that would train her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:33.30,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.56,0:07:35.56,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me work here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:37.34,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:40.06,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents are against this, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.26,0:07:41.14,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.13,0:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:45.89,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Being a chef isn't as easy as you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:48.44,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you'll be able to keep it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.42,0:07:50.44,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:55.45,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Then show me what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.31,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.33,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,It's rather thick, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.26,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.01,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appalled that you decided to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.01,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become a chef with this level of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.60,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,She still has a lot she needs to work on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager, Mr. Ren,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.73,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,could you let her work here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until she can at least be of some use?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Although she's still a rookie,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that she has the right mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.65,Default,Sui,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Mr. Ren?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.54,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge of \Ntraining her in the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:52.13,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:55.01,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking so dumbfounded for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:08:57.01,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Chefs need to wake up early,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.76,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,kitchen hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.95,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:04.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.79,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Check up on her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:14.64,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Nako and I will finish the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:15.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:37.65,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Minko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.99,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have duties to attend to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because \NI'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:50.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.13,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can work at Fukuya too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.45,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not with my skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sure you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:06.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru will recommend you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Just like he did \Nwhen you first came here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.46,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Tohru'll be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,glad to work with you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.51,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:19.47,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can go and work at Fukuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.83,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I got a job here thanks to Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.38,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much I need to repay Tohru,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager, Mr. Ren, \Nand the inn itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:32.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But you were just saying that\Nyou wanted to go to Fukuya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:35.48,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You misunderstood me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:37.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.50,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's work, love, or personal matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:41.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,you're giving it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cheer you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You need to chase after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.17,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You can't work without him, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:57.73,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Get out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.49,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Get out, balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,M- Minko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've been locked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minko must really like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:17.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Falling in love with someone \Nmust be incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko must be feeling the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:24.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.88,0:11:29.43,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.43,0:11:31.58,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,After all, \Nit's just a regional festival-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:36.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I didn't say it was pointless, Takako.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.56,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,She screams about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:41.80,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, where did I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:44.97,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:47.63,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be working?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.90,0:11:49.64,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.39,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind lending me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:52.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know when you find the bonbori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.66,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Just look in any of the boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:01.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:07.02,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You know what they look like, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:14.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't \Nunderstand a single thing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.89,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo! That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is this for the Bonbori Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.26,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's this at the bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.30,0:12:34.66,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wish card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:37.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A wish card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.36,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,If you write your wish on it
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tie it to the bonbori,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:51.54,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,a god will use it to illuminate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his path home back to Izumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.40,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,and in return, he'll grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:58.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.81,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But only hardworking people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will have their wishes granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:05.14,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,People like you who don't work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't have their wishes come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hardworking people...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:14.75,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,But will we really get more customers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we make our bonboris look more modern?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.24,0:13:20.86,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I'm \Ngoing to disobey Takako's orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So hardworking people will
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,get their wishes granted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.15,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:28.32,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.91,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Balut! Balut! Balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:35.27,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot doesn't understand anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:46.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go and drag Tohru back!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.71,0:13:50.47,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He may be sharp-tongued,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.73,0:13:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's more determined than
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,anyone, and kinder than anyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:13:58.85,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He may appear abrupt and cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in reality he treasures the people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,working here and his job more than anyone else, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And he has this much hair,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his eyes are slanted upwards, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:14.13,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.95,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru was invited to Fukuya \Nbecause of his skill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:21.41,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what \Nan honor that is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:24.13,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.85,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I wish him all the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:31.35,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want to get in his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You balut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:37.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You like him, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.22,0:14:41.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll go to Fukuya myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:44.05,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! \NHow will that solve anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you're such a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:50.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I have the feeling that'll allow me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to work hard towards something as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:56.56,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be impossible \Nto drag him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Then, we'll ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for help from the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:04.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.33,0:15:05.38,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.80,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:28.60,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:38.17,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a ba-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.76,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.61,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Gr-and-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:15:59.03,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,How many times must I tell you to
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,call me "Manager," Yuina?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.97,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Sor-ry, Gr-and-ma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.79,0:16:06.15,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.30,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,There... seems... to be
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something... going on by the... entr-ance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk to the manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:18.04,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.46,0:16:19.54,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:21.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.82,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you from Shijima's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here today \Nbecause I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:28.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Please give Tohru back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:30.18,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're all horrible at Fukuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:33.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You have a large inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,lots of cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:38.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and a very pretty granddaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:40.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to\Nsteal one of our staff away from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:43.90,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,What's this girl talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you got an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso needs Tohru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:48.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:50.33,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru's gone back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Where to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.83,0:16:53.86,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:55.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Kissuiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.96,0:16:56.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.93,0:17:00.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,As a helper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:10.67,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,One of our chefs was out with a cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.57,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,so the head chef \Nof Kissuiso lent Tohru to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:15.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:19.41,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I said that with a fake \NHakata accent today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:21.35,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Did you understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what it all was about...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:30.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Then you and Tohru aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:31.49,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:33.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You were with him on his motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:37.66,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I wanted to ride it, so he let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.81,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, what should I do about the helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.81,0:17:44.55,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Tohru won't be coming over anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.83,0:17:46.29,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want it, Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.68,Default,Yuina,0000,0000,0000,,I've decorated it a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.68,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can still use it to ride a motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:55.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever need it, I'll let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:02.47,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.37,0:18:06.13,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana, Tohru came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.73,0:18:09.32,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Working at Fukuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.19,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck came up with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:17.00,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't he \Nuse his time to write his
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,erotica instead \Nof spreading dumb rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:23.54,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Ren...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.66,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What if... just what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.26,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I actually went to work for Fukuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.79,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop you! \NNext time, I'll definitely stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.84,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.34,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.81,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Go check how many \Nvegetables we still have in stock, Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.00,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:44.63,Default,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,And while you're at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,organize the food supplies in the storeroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:51.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy for Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:53.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:00.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.04,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get on my motorbike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:05.74,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You're always in my way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though none of the\Nright parts of you are sticking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:13.26,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in your way anymore, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go on home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.51,0:19:16.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.30,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You went all the way there to bring me\Nback, yet you're acting like this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.34,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,So, when are you going to hold a farewell party for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That was-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:28.68,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,So, in the end, you're the only\None who tried to stop me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.21,0:19:33.78,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's better than no one, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a sensitive nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:43.60,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a big deal \Nuntil Mr. Ren tries to stop me himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:56.05,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tohru went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:57.46,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:00.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still not very fond of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:07.72,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like Tohru had a good experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:11.23,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Now he'll have somewhere to go to when we shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:11.96,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:13.25,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:17.23,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Enishi, call them later and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.02,Default,Mana,0000,0000,0000,,Shigeko, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:21.60,Default,Enishi,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.75,0:20:27.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:30.05,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You did run around a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.57,0:20:34.29,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad \Nhe wasn't taken away, Minko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.46,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:42.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be with him for a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.56,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Minchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.47,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,But in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to write down \Nwhat you want me to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.49,0:20:52.39,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.98,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Nako told me that you wanted a nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.90,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,If you write it on the wish card, \NI'll call you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:01.74,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:08.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.96,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that \NI'd have to come up with one myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.82,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"Nakochi," "Minchi..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.82,0:21:19.10,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"Ohachi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe "Hanachi" is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But that's too similar to "hibachi chicken!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:26.12,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.60,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.14,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:32.94,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.94,0:21:34.53,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,You're too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.53,0:21:37.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll come up with one really quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:37.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one more chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:38.48,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:39.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
